item.content:encoded: If there’s one lesson to take from people living in small spaces, it’s that even the tiniest rooms can be stylish and look far from cramped. One-wall kitchens are a perfect example of how to make the most of small kitchen design. As their name suggests, these small kitchens only occupy a single wall, but in doing so, they leave space for items like dining tables, bar carts, and breakfast bars.
